docs.title: mris_register
docs.description: This program registers a surface to an average surface template.

docs.title: Target
docs.description: The data to register to. A template file for average surface or a single-subject's surface.

docs.title: Output file name
docs.description: Output surface file to capture registration. Example: {hemi}.sphere.reg

docs.title: Single subject target
docs.description: Treats target argument as a single subject's surface not a template file.

docs.title: Add frame values
docs.description: Add field with location in the atlas.

docs.title: Inflated initial alignment flag
docs.description: Use inflated surface for initial alignment.

docs.title: Inflated surface name
docs.description: Uses this name for inflated surface for initial alignment.

docs.title: Label file
docs.description: Specify a manual label to align with atlas label.

docs.title: Overlay values
docs.description: Adds a variable to the atlas from overlay file, smoothing it specified number of times.

docs.title: Starting registration file
docs.description: Start registration with coordinates from file.

docs.title: Jacobian output file
docs.description: Write out jacobian of mapping to the specified file.

docs.title: Curvature flag
docs.description: Use smoothwm curvature for final alignment.

docs.title: Momentum
docs.description: Chooses integration_type = INTEGRATE_MOMENTUM and sets momentum value.

docs.title: Number of angles per scale
docs.description: Set number of angles/search per scale.

docs.title: No curvature flag
docs.description: Do not use smoothwm curvature for final alignment.

docs.title: Number of surfaces
docs.description: Use specified number of surfaces/curvatures for alignment.

docs.title: Remove negative
docs.description: Remove negative triangles with iterative smoothing if non-zero.

docs.title: Reverse flag
docs.description: Mirror image reverse brain before morphing.

docs.title: Registration file
docs.description: Extract rotational components from registration file.

docs.title: Scale
docs.description: Scales distances by the specified value.

docs.title: Search flag
docs.description: Integrate with binary search line minimization.

docs.title: Topology flag
docs.description: Preserves the topology of positive area triangles.

docs.title: Vertex number
docs.description: Supplies a vertex number for diagnostics.

docs.title: Vector flag
docs.description: Prints help for Multiframe mode, listing field names and numbers.

docs.title: mris_register
docs.description: This program registers a surface to an average surface template.
